    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="开篇介绍"><a href="#开篇介绍" class="headerlink" title="开篇介绍"></a>开篇介绍</h3><ol><li><p><strong>什么是计算机？为什么要有计算机？</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">代替人力的一种机器</span><br><span class="line">计算机诞生的早期目的是科学计算 将人类从重复繁杂的工作中解放出来</span><br><span class="line">第一台计算机诞生于1946年美国宾夕法尼亚大学</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>什么是编程语言？什么是编程？为什么要编程？什么是程序？</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">编程语言就是人的和计算机沟通的语言</span><br><span class="line">编程就是让计算机按照人的指令步骤做事</span><br><span class="line">让计算机取代人力</span><br><span class="line">程序就是一段有序的指令集合 一堆代码文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>程序分为两类</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">应用程序</span><br><span class="line">操作系统(协调管理计算机硬件资源和应用软件资源的控制程序)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>计算机系统三层结构</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">应用程序(应用软件)</span><br><span class="line">-----</span><br><span class="line">操作系统（系统软件）</span><br><span class="line">-----</span><br><span class="line">计算机硬件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="/images/6.JPG" alt="计算机系统结构图"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">计算机系统结构图</span></div></div></li><li><p><strong>程序的开发流程</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">需求分析阶段 </span><br><span class="line">1.PM：调研市场，需求分析，原型草图</span><br><span class="line">2.PM召集所有相关技术人员开需求分析会：明确需求</span><br><span class="line">项目开发阶段 </span><br><span class="line">1,项目设计:</span><br><span class="line">  UE与PM产品经理 产出交互原型图</span><br><span class="line">  UI根据原型图  产出设计图</span><br><span class="line">  FE前端开发 前端设计</span><br><span class="line">  RD后端开发 后端技术设计</span><br><span class="line">  QA测试人员 测试用例设计</span><br><span class="line">  OP运维人员 运维架构设计</span><br><span class="line"> 2,项目开发</span><br><span class="line"> 前后端分头开发</span><br><span class="line"> 合并</span><br><span class="line">项目测试阶段 </span><br><span class="line">1,开发人员进行code review 审查代码</span><br><span class="line">2,开发人员自测 改bug</span><br><span class="line">3,QA专用测试 改bug</span><br><span class="line">项目上线阶段</span><br><span class="line">1,运维人员编写上线方案</span><br><span class="line">2,测试</span><br><span class="line">环境</span><br><span class="line">测试环境</span><br><span class="line">staging环境</span><br><span class="line">线上环境</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="/images/7.JPG" alt="程序开发流程图"/></div><div class="image-meta"><span class="image-caption center">程序开发流程图</span></div></div></li><li><p><strong>运维职责</strong></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">保证程序不间断运行 围绕计算机结构三层,做好监控 遇到问题提前解决</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">备份 做好数据备份 遇到问题方便回滚</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">优化性能：提升用户访问速度</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>运维人员原则：</strong></p><div class="tag-plugin note" color="red"><div class="body"><p>简单易用高效</p></div></div></li></ol><h4 id="去IOE运动"><a href="#去IOE运动" class="headerlink" title="去IOE运动"></a>去IOE运动</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**去IOE运动的本质是防止垄断**</span></span><br><span class="line">IBM：服务器===》 dell服务器，云主机</span><br><span class="line">甲骨文oracle：数据库管理软件===mysql(marriadb)</span><br><span class="line">EMC：存储===》 自定义存储 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​</p><div class="tag-plugin poetry"><div class="content"><div class="title">清平调一</div><div class="meta"><span>李白</span></div><div class="body"><p>云想衣裳花想容，春风拂槛露华浓。</p><p>若非群玉山头见，会向瑶台月下逢。</p></div><div class="footer">诗词节选</div></div></div>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
